\taxon{Audience}
\title{The categorical logician}
\import{prelude}

\p{The \defcase{categorical logician} is a reader who is comfortable with modern approaches to the categorical semantics of type theory, such as:}

\ul{
  \li{[[shulman-2016-categorical]]}
  \li{[[kovacs-2022-typetheoretic]]}
  \li{[[uemura-2021-abstract]]}
}

\p{The categorical logician also has a reasonable grasp of topos theory and 2-category theory.}
